Create Report Page 1: Dashboard - part 2 4

Step 7. Funnel showcasing Top 10 Total Discharges by Diagnosis

Step 7. Funnel Chart showcasing Top 10 Discharges by Diagnosis

a) Create a funnel chart

b) Add DRG Definition to Group and Total Discharges to Values.


c)Filter by top 10 by adding a visual filter on DRG Definition.  Choose Top N as filter type and 10 as unit. Add Total Discharges as "By value" and click Apply filter.


d) Format the chart by changing color, data labels position and removing title.

e) Add title and summary Text box . Edit font, size and color.


Step 8. Stacked Bar Chart showcasing Top 10 Total Payment by Diagnosis

- Additional insight on medicare vs out of pocket by utilizing two values

a) Create a Stacked Bar Chart

b) Add DRG Definition to Axis, add Average Medicare Payment to Value and add Average Patient out of Pocket to Value


c) Filter by top 10 by adding a visual filter on DRG Definition.  Choose Top N as filter type and 10 as unit. Add Total Payment as "By value" and click Apply filter.


d) Format the chart by changing color, removing legend and title.


e) Add title and summary Text box . Edit font, size and color.
